强沟通，共同应对全球性挑战。 王毅还就中美两军交往，金融、科技、人文交流合作，中国投资环境、市场准入以及中东局势、乌克兰危机等与会人员关心的问题同大家深入交流。 座谈会由美国阿斯彭战略小组主办。王毅同美国战略界人士座谈：「通往旧金山」不能靠「自动驾驶」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-31618b1e60b657fafebf387f641f12c8_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628269404"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5a3prZXhm+1REAMaCTEwMTg5NDE4NCCrnfepBjAAOMIBQBZyCTYyODI2OTQwNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1698743059.780318", "card_id": "Q_627592180", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你最喜欢哪种虚构的时空旅行方式？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627592180"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5a3prZXhm+1REAMaCTEwMTc0Mzc1NyD1p96pBjAAOE9AF3IJNjI3NTkyMTgweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1698743059.780566", "card_id": "Q_628144367", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在你看过的动画、漫画中，有哪些平时没啥用关键时候却很有用的技能或能力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5bb6fc9caffb4119db350e9315cb2b07_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/628144367"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5a3prZXhm+1REAMaCTEwMTg2NjUyMSDKo/GpBjAAOC9AGHIJNjI4MTQ0MzY3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1698743059.780762", "card_id": "Q_628479186",